{"tid":2257662,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"28奈米夠用了！新款龍芯3A4000獨顯筆電發表，13.3英吋、連顯卡也28奈米","createTime":"2020-10-25T11:10:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-25T12:59:10.000Z","uid":28114,"like":9,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"10b3bf26df98809be6a1c80b59a1887861517020","tid":2257662,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T11:10:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn1.techbang.com/system/excerpt_images/82024/special_headline/3f3c5fa95f124926574ac49740e164ae.jpg?1603437557\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn1.techbang.com%2Fsystem%2Fexcerpt_images%2F82024%2Fspecial_headline%2F3f3c5fa95f124926574ac49740e164ae.jpg%3F1603437557&h=08e42889&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n前兩天我們報導過，中國晶片龍頭「龍芯中科技術」董事長胡偉武講到還需要十年才有可能趕上台積電的製程技術，並且表示「不要再想著美國做5奈米、誰做5奈米，別想那些，14奈米夠用了，28奈米夠用了，90.9%的應用都夠了。」<br />\n<br />\n而現在，中國廠商「比亞迪電子」就推出了採用「龍芯3A4000」這款處理器的筆電，而「龍芯3A4000」就是龍芯去年推出採用28奈米製程的處理器。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn1.techbang.com/system/images/574269/original/7cff88f815f0c552210a4bf86d78f0d3.jpg?1603436355\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn1.techbang.com%2Fsystem%2Fimages%2F574269%2Foriginal%2F7cff88f815f0c552210a4bf86d78f0d3.jpg%3F1603436355&h=9833bfbf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這款筆電整機重量1.55kg，採用13.3吋窄邊框螢幕。處理器採用龍芯3A4000，這是他們最新一代的處理器核心（代號GS464V），相比上一代龍芯3A3000性能提升100%。而且這是一款獨顯筆電，顯卡一樣是中國國產的「 景嘉微JM7201」，一樣是28奈米製程，廠商表示性能完全滿足日常辦公的多情境需求。<br />\n<br />\n接口方面，擁有兩個USB 3.0接口，一個USB C接口，一個HDMI影片輸出接口，一個Audio接口，搭載4個喇叭實現全景外放，並且搭載自家比亞迪65Wh高容量電池。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn1.techbang.com/system/images/574270/original/d88059dde43caa354c1de2130179783f.jpg?1603436557\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn1.techbang.com%2Fsystem%2Fimages%2F574270%2Foriginal%2Fd88059dde43caa354c1de2130179783f.jpg%3F1603436557&h=6aeb61bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n龍芯處理器並不支援安裝Windows，因此僅能安裝中國「國產OS」，其實就是一些從Linux修改而來的系統，或是使用者可以自己去安裝不同版本的Linux。<br />\n<br />\n龍芯3A4000主頻為1.8GHz-2.0GHz，每個CPU晶片包含4個獨立的處理器核。官方表示效能相當於AMD同樣採用28奈米製程的&quot;挖掘機&quot;Excavator處理器。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.techbang.com/posts/82024-byd-push-dragon-core-3a4000-pen-133-inches-with-domestic\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.techbang.com%2Fposts%2F82024-byd-push-dragon-core-3a4000-pen-133-inches-with-domestic&d=FHegwWfkEdb3mv0CWz72PUyCzF7GSvQxQofikz39bzk%3D&h=966c4204\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.techbang.com/posts/82024-byd-push-dragon-core-3a4000-pen-133-inches-with-domestic</a>"},{"pid":"9831400dc697e93741558829fe185aeeec2ec8c1","tid":2257662,"uid":28114,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T11:11:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/d/d6/Fool56k.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2Fd%2Fd6%2FFool56k.JPG&h=9bb8b677&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4a71447edb65bc53fabe2482c32888c27280a4db","tid":2257662,"uid":28114,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T11:13:38.000Z","msg":"驚閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />支那Joe一贏，又會有5nm用了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6243cbad0795b39182bbd648716108ebbff9526","tid":2257662,"uid":156913,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"9831400dc697e93741558829fe185aeeec2ec8c1","tid":2257662,"uid":28114,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T11:11:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/d/d6/Fool56k.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2Fd%2Fd6%2FFool56k.JPG&h=9bb8b677&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T11:13:45.000Z","msg":"等高手合體<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/business/page/800/2020/10/19/phpLilgqC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpl